title: Fagor LUX Multicooker 101
description: The Fagor LUX Multicooker is a pressure cooker, slow cooker, rice cooker with different functions for White rice, Brown rice and Risotto, and a yogurt maker!. It also features cooking assist functions such as Brown, Sauté, Steam, Simmer and also keeps your food warm.  This is  truly a one-of-a-kind multifunctional cooker!

transcripts: The Fagor LUX multicooker takes the place of for cooking vessels it can be used as a pressure cooker a slow cooker a rice cooker and a yogurt maker in addition to these four programs deluxe also has four cooking this functions brown, saute, simmer and steam. The LUX also has a keep warm function and a time delay first lets look at the lid its equipped with the pressure regulator knob the safety valve and the gasket. This is the pressure regulator knob it has three settings pressure, steam and clean. The removable cooking pot is where all your ingredients will go the pot has a ceramic coating that is stain resistant scratch-resistant nonstick and allows for even heat distribution on the base you have the condensation collector. The LUX comes with a users manual and a recipe booklet with 12 delicious recipes and a link to a free digital download of a cookbook with more than 75 recipes.
